|==============================
|ffeil=modiwl001b
|{*Notes:*}
meddwn = {mjperson}{mjself}{mjpointleft}{mjmouth}
meddit = {mjperson}{mjpointleft}{mjmouth}
|meddai = {mjperson}{mjmouth}
|
`"Helo! Sut` mae`!" meddai Adda.
`"Helo! Sut` mae`!" meddai Bethan.
`"Ti` yn` iawn`?" meddai Adda.
`"Fi` yn` iawn`, diolch`!" meddai Bethan, "a thi`?"
`"Fi` yn` iawn` hefyd`, diolch`," meddai Adda.
`"Neis` i` gael_cwrdd` a^` thi`!" meddai Bethan.
`"Ti` hefyd`! Neis` i` gael_cwrdd` a^` thi`!" meddai Adda.
`"Hwyl` te`!" meddai Bethan.
`"Hwyl`! Wela` di` yn` fuan`!" meddai Adda.
